### II. Patent Claim by Public Record

This publication constitutes a **public, timestamped, cryptographically verifiable patent claim**.

| Proof Layer | Value |
|---|---|
| **Merkle Root / Tree Hash** | *(populated automatically on first push — see `.timestamps/`)* |
